#: src/ui/moreInfo.ui:16
msgid "More Information"
msgstr "Mere information"

#. Ignore the ugly formatting. New lines are literal.
#: src/ui/moreInfo.ui:34
msgid ""
"You're using <a href=\"https://firewalld.org/\">firewalld</a> as your "
"firewall. One of the nice features about firewalld is that it supports "
"different zones (sets of firewall rules). You may have a firewall zone "
"configured for home use, and a different zone for public networks.\n"
"\n"
"You're using <a href=\"https://networkmanager.dev/\">NetworkManager</a> for "
"network configuration. NetworkManager integrates well with firewalld and can "
"<a href=\"https://firewalld.org/documentation/zone/connections-interfaces-"
"and-sources.html\">set the firewalld zone for an interface based on the "
"connection</a>. This means your firewall rules can automatically change "
"depending on your network connection.\n"
"\n"
"Bouncer is designed to make this easier for you. It opens a window when you "
"connect to a new network, allowing you to choose the appropriate firewall "
"zone. If you're not sure what to choose, you should probably choose the "
"option that matches where you are. The safest option is usually 'public'. If "
"you don't want to change anything, click 'Exit'.\n"
"\n"
"You can read more about Bouncer <a href=\"https://github.com/justinrdonnelly/"
"bouncer\">here</a>."
msgstr ""
"Du bruger <a href=\"https://firewalld.org/\">firewalld</a> som din firewall. "
"En af de gode ting ved firewalld er, at den understøtter forskellige zoner "
"(sæt af firewall-regler). Du har måske konfigureret en firewall-zone til "
"brug derhjemme og en anden zone til offentlige netværk.\n"
"\n"
"Du bruger <a href=\"https://networkmanager.dev/\">NetworkManager</a> til "
"netværkskonfiguration. NetworkManager integreres godt med firewalld og kan "
"<a href=\"https://firewalld.org/documentation/zone/connections-interfaces-"
"and-sources.html\">indstille firewalld-zonen for en grænseflade baseret på "
"forbindelsen</a>. Det betyder, at dine firewall-regler automatisk kan ændres "
"afhængigt af din netværksforbindelse.\n"
"\n"
"Bouncer er designet til at gøre dette lettere for dig. Det åbner et vindue, "
"når du opretter forbindelse til et nyt netværk, så du kan vælge den passende "
"firewall-zone. Hvis du ikke er sikker på, hvad du skal vælge, bør du "
"sandsynligvis vælge den indstilling, der passer til, hvor du befinder dig. "
"Den sikreste indstilling er normalt ›offentlig‹. Hvis du ikke ønsker at "
"ændre noget, skal du klikke på ›Afslut‹.\n"
"\n"
"Du kan læse mere om Bouncer <a href=\"https://github.com/justinrdonnelly/"
"bouncer\">her</a>."

